**Job Title:** Administrative Officer

**Responsibilities:**

- Be the first point of contact for student and visitor enquiries 
- Provide effective course, student and academic administrative support to the Business School
- Ensure effective communication processes between Schools, Faculty, and other departments of the University

**Skills & Competencies:**

- Understanding of the employer's mission and values 
- Ability to actively contribute to values and mission 
- Ability to handle inquiries
- Capability to provide effective administrative support
- Good communication skills

**Keywords:**

- First point of contact
- Student and visitor enquiries
- Course, student and academic administrative support
- Business School
- Communication processes
- Schools, Faculty, University departments
- Mission and values
- Active contribution
